reviews.text: My friends, 2 staffs and I have come to this place and that one of the staff ordered turkey burger with lettuce, tomato, and French fries, and the other staff ordered a bagel with cream cheese. The service was wonderful, and the atmosphere was that there were no one there till the group came in. The people in there were nice and friendly.
